subject: NCAA Basketball Championships (Women)
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Unlike the N.C.A.A. men’s tournament, one powerhouse stands out in the women’s field: Baylor. The Lady Bears, led by Brittney Griner, have won 30 straight games.
